{"data":[{"date":"14:53 12/07","title":"T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Croatia \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u1eebng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Dalic","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/tong-thong-croatia-dien-mung-thay-tro-dalic.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"4164","checkdouble":"191033"},{"date":"16:13 12/07","title":"Si\u00eau m\u1eabu Croatia n\u00f3ng b\u1ecfng tin \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/12/sieu-mau-croatia-nong-bong-tin-doi-nha-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Si\u00eau m\u1eabu Nives Celsius quy\u1ebft c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u1ed9 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Kolinda, tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 Croatia s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Kolinda Grabar-Kitarovic \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup 2018, khi lu\u00f4n ch\u00e1y h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi \u0110TQG Croatia.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nN\u1eef T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng xinh \u0111\u1eb9p lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i, v\u00e0 b\u00e0 c\u0169ng xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n ho\u1eb7c v\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 chia vui v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Croatia sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Croartia nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c: si\u00eau m\u1eabu Nives Celsius.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Nives Celsius l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 xa l\u1ea1 v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Croatia. \u1ede nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, Nives lu\u00f4n \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Croatia b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ea7y g\u1ee3i c\u1ea3m.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f4 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t r\u1ea5t gi\u1ecfi trong vi\u1ec7c \"troll\" c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 sau nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. Nives Celsius l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao l\u00e0ng gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed Croatia, t\u1eeb kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh ca h\u00e1t, s\u00e1ng t\u00e1c v\u00e0 truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb9p 36 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y t\u1eebng k\u1ebft h\u00f4n v\u1edbi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Dino Drpic - ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 1 tr\u1eadn kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Croatia. Tuy nhi\u00ean, hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 li d\u1ecb v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2014, sau 9 n\u0103m chung s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 v\u1edbi nhau 2 m\u1eb7t con.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNives chia s\u1ebb, c\u00f4 c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c m\u00e0 Croatia \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p, nh\u01b0ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u0103ng quang. Theo l\u1eddi t\u00e2m s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Nives, c\u00f4 hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fa \u00fd v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o s\u1ee9c h\u00fat gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Kolinda.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/nives-celsius-2.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/nives-celsius-1.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/nives-celsius-8.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/nives-celsius-7.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/nives-celsius-5.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/nives-celsius-4.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/nives-celsius-3.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4163","checkdouble":"191046"},{"date":"15:09 12/07","title":"10 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 khi Ronaldo chuy\u1ec3n sang Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/10-ky-luc-co-the-bi-pha-khi-ronaldo-chuyen-sang-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 sau M.U v\u00e0 Real Madrid, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn CLB Juventus l\u00e0m b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u0111ang ch\u1edd ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 ph\u00e1 khi \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n t\u1edbi Turin.</h2><h2>1. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u00f3 tr\u1ecdn b\u1ed9 3 danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Anh, T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 Italia</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u00ean b\u1ee5c vinh quang nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00e0 Premier League, La Liga v\u00e0 Serie A.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 Ronaldo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ebfu c\u00f9ng Juve gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam Scudetto trong m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi m\u00e0 'B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0' \u0111ang n\u1eafm k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 7 l\u1ea7n li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2011/12 t\u1edbi nay.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus lan thu 6 lien tiep doat Scudetto\" title=\"Juventus l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 6 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111o\u1ea1t Scudetto\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/5/22/juventus-30-crotone-thien-duong-thu-6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Sang Juventus, Ronaldo&nbsp;s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch 3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>2. V\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League v\u1edbi 3 CLB kh\u00e1c nhau</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00fang 1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League v\u1edbi 3 CLB kh\u00e1c nhau trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i AC Milan, Clarence Seedorf. C\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y t\u1eebng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u1edbi Ajax, Real Madrid v\u00e0 AC Milan.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu CR7 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u00f9ng Juve, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 anh s\u1ebd b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Seedorf m\u00e0 anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League c\u00f9ng 3 CLB kh\u00e1c nhau l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t (6 l\u1ea7n) so v\u1edbi 4 l\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Seedorf.</p>\r\n<h2>3. V\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi 6 l\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c, CR7 s\u1ebd s\u00e1nh ngang v\u1edbi k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Real Paco Gento - ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia 6 danh hi\u1ec7u C1 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1956 \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 1965. Tuy nhi\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00ean th\u00ec Ronaldo v\u1eabn \u0111ang 'v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i' v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap s\u1edf h\u1eefu.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo huong loi neu toi Juventus\" title=\"Ronaldo h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i n\u1ebfu t\u1edbi Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/emre-can-hao-huc-truoc-co-hoi-choi-bong-cung-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ronaldo ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam 1 danh hi\u1ec7u Champions League n\u1ebfu t\u1edbi Juventus</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>4. Gi\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u QBV nh\u1ea5t</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Roanldo v\u00e0 Messi \u0111ang c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c gi\u00e0nh 5 QBV th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Tuy nhi\u00ean CR7 \u0111ang c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1edfi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League 2017/18 c\u00f9ng m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, Ronaldo chuy\u1ec3n sang Juventus s\u1ebd gi\u00fap anh c\u00f3 th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 'ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m' trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh&nbsp;danh hi\u1ec7u QBV th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m nay l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</p>\r\n<h2>5. Gi\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng nh\u1ea5t</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh sau nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i M.U (m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng 2007/08) v\u00e0 Real Madrid (c\u00e1c m\u00f9a 2010/11, 2013/14 v\u00e0 2014/15). Chuy\u1ec3n sang m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh b\u1edbt kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t h\u01a1n nh\u01b0 Serie A, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 CR7 gi\u00e0nh Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 5 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>6. Ghi b\u00e0n nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ea1i Serie A</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111ang thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Higuain v\u1edbi 36 b\u00e0n trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Napoli. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7n nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng Ronaldo t\u1eebng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c n\u00e0y \u1edf c\u00e1c m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i (2010-11, 2011-12, 2014-15).</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo la cau thu dat gia nhat lich su Juventus.\" title=\"Ronaldo l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Juventus.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/10-ky-luc-co-the-bi-pha-khi-ronaldo-chuyen-sang-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ronaldo \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c ghi b\u00e0n nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ea1i Serie A cho Juventus.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>7. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Juventus ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Serie A</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1eafm gi\u1eef k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n cho Juventus l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ferenc Herzer v\u1edbi 35 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 1925/26. N\u1ebfu Ronaldo ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n anh ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd x\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed5 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i g\u1ea7n 100 n\u0103m n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<h2>8. Ghi nhi\u1ec1u hat-trick b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Champions League</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 7 c\u00fa hat-trick b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 khi l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Juve, Ronaldo ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1eadp th\u00eam nh\u1eefng hat-trick b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ed1 1.</p>\r\n<h2>9. V\u01b0\u1ee3t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c l\u1eadp hat-trick b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i Serie A</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed5 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c l\u1eadp hat-trick b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i Serie A l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u1edbi Ronaldo b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0 Gunnar Nordahl v\u00e0 Giuseppe Meazza \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 17 l\u1ea7n l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, Ronaldo c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa l\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed5 n\u1ebfu anh c\u1ee9 ghi trung b\u00ecnh 4 \u0111\u1ebfn 5 c\u00fa hat-trick trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</p>\r\n<h2>10. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf 3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi khi ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i M.U c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u1edf Real Madrid. V\u00e0 anh s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf 3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u n\u1ebfu ghi b\u00e0n s\u00f2n s\u00f2n \u1edf Juve.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 John Charles v\u00e0 Christian Vieri \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u00e0y v\u1edbi hai gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/day-3-muc-tieu-hang-dau-duoc-real-nham-thay-ronaldo-180-190973.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/day-3-muc-tieu-hang-dau-duoc-real-nham-thay-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/day-3-muc-tieu-hang-dau-duoc-real-nham-thay-ronaldo-180-190973.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! 3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real nh\u1eafm thay Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 \u0111ang \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Cristiano Ronaldo, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Los Blancos.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/infographics/infographics-cristiano-ronaldo-chia-tay-real-madrid-ra-di-de-lai-nhung-gi-406-190961.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/infographics-cristiano-ronaldo-chia-tay-real-madrid-ra-di-de-lai-nhung-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/infographics/infographics-cristiano-ronaldo-chia-tay-real-madrid-ra-di-de-lai-nhung-gi-406-190961.html\">Infographics: Cristiano Ronaldo chia tay Real Madrid - Ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 vi\u1ebft n\u00ean m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, d\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u00e2u, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n gi\u1eef m\u1ed9t l\u00f2ng trung th\u00e0nh...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/goc-nhin-cristiano-ronaldo-gia-nhap-juventus-176-190940.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/Gareth-Bale-roi-Real-khong-the-xay-ra-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/goc-nhin-cristiano-ronaldo-gia-nhap-juventus-176-190940.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: V\u00ec b\u1ecb M.U ph\u1ee5 b\u1ea1c, Ronaldo m\u1edbi \u0111i theo &ldquo;B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m&rdquo; Juventus</span><br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, th\u00f4ng tin Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1. &ldquo;B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0&rdquo; kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a CR7 m\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 Man...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4162","checkdouble":"191027"},{"date":"15:32 12/07","title":"Juve s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p CR7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/12/world-cup-2018-vang-nhung-cu-vo-le-nga-ban-den-doc-dao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Juve l\u00e0 CLB cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, sau khi si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\r\n</h2><h2>CR7 gia nh\u1eadp Serie A<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">112 tri\u1ec7u euro l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ebfn Juventus ph\u1ea3i chi ra \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Cristiano Ronaldo &ndash; si\u00eau sao \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi danh hi\u1ec7u t\u1ea1i Real Madrid, v\u00e0 \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi. 9 n\u0103m t\u1ea1i Los Blancos, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Serie A v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Nh\u1eefng n\u0103m th\u00e1ng \u1edf Real Madrid, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac nh\u1ea5t trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi t\u00f4i. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng bi\u1ebft \u01a1n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 v\u00ec t\u00ecnh y\u00eau m\u00e0 t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1edf ra giai \u0111o\u1ea1n m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u00f4i y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 h\u00e3y hi\u1ec3u cho quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y&rdquo; &ndash; CR7 cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juve l\u00e0 CLB cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo\" title=\"Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/world-cup-2018-vang-nhung-cu-vo-le-nga-ban-den-doc-dao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juve l\u00e0 CLB cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Jorge Mendes c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo: &ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng cho anh \u1ea5y. Juve l\u00e0 CLB cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a CLB, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111o\u1ea1n k\u1ebft tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Ronaldo.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Xin c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Andrea Agnelli, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ronaldo, v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea3o c\u00f9ng Real Madrid. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft \u01a1n G\u0110\u0110H Beppe Marotta v\u00ec s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y&rdquo; &ndash; si\u00eau c\u00f2 Jorge Mendes cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cris Ronaldo \u0111ang \u0111i ngh\u1ec9 \u1edf Hy L\u1ea1p sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018, v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft CLB Juventus v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 Hai tu\u1ea7n sau. V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Real Madrid, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i b\u1ea1o chi trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8, \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/10-ky-luc-co-the-bi-pha-khi-ronaldo-chuyen-sang-juventus-176-191027.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/10-ky-luc-co-the-bi-pha-khi-ronaldo-chuyen-sang-juventus.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/10-ky-luc-co-the-bi-pha-khi-ronaldo-chuyen-sang-juventus-176-191027.html\">10 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 khi Ronaldo chuy\u1ec3n sang Juventus</span><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 sau M.U v\u00e0 Real Madrid, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn CLB Juventus l\u00e0m b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u0111ang ch\u1edd ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/quan-diem-cristiano-ronaldo-toi-juventus-va-su-ngan-can-cua-mourinho-mu-172-191022.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/quan-diem-cristiano-ronaldo-toi-juventus-va-su-ngan-can-cua-mourinho-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/quan-diem-cristiano-ronaldo-toi-juventus-va-su-ngan-can-cua-mourinho-mu-172-191022.html\">Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: &ldquo;K\u1ebb hai m\u1eb7t&rdquo; Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 ng\u0103n Ronaldo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U</span><br>\r\nThay v\u00ec tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Man United, Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus. Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do HLV Jose Mourinho d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ec3...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4161","checkdouble":"191028"},{"date":"15:22 12/07","title":"VFF b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd lo\u1ea1i th\u1eb3ng tay U23 \u00dac kh\u1ecfi gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/vff-bat-ngo-loai-thang-tay-u23-uc-khoi-giai-tu-hung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eddi tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam song cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0110T U23 \u00dac \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i do kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ph\u00eda VFF.</h2><h2>VFF b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd lo\u1ea1i th\u1eb3ng tay U23 \u00dac v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1edbi 8 t\u1edbi, L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee9ng ra t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng quy t\u1ee5 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m 'thu\u1ed1c th\u1eed li\u1ec1u cao' cho \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"VFF b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd lo\u1ea1i th\u1eb3ng tay U23 \u00dac kh\u1ecfi gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"VFF b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd lo\u1ea1i th\u1eb3ng tay U23 \u00dac kh\u1ecfi gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/giai-quoc-te-u-23-3_emlc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1ea5t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dac</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi l\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0110T U23 Uzbekistan, U23 Oman v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ea1i D\u01b0\u01a1ng U23 \u00dac. Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai do kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Do L\u0110B\u0110 \u00dac kh\u00f4ng thu x\u1ebfp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y n\u00ean h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i U19 tham d\u1ef1. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf, BTC gi\u1ea3i \u0111ang t\u00ednh t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd thay \u0111\u1ed9i Australia b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U23 t\u1eebng l\u1ecdt \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 U23 Ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, trong th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm gi\u00fap U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u00edch l\u0169y th\u00eam nh\u1eefng kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ASIAD.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4160","checkdouble":"191038"},{"date":"16:30 12/07","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/6/hlv-park-hang-seo-co-nguy-co-mat-tro-cung-tai-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u01b0a b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u1ea3n tr\u1edf trung v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, l\u00fac n\u00e0y th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a NHM v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea7m c\u01a1 ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c n\u00e0y, trong su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian qua, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i d\u1ef1 kh\u00e1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u V-League \u0111\u1ec3 quan s\u00e1t c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/5/HLV-Park-Hang-Seo-co-nguy-co-mat-tro-cung-tai-ASIAD-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi ASIAD 2018 v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ngo\u00e0i s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23, s\u1ebd c\u00f3 3 su\u1ea5t cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y Park t\u00ecm ra nh\u1eefng m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean lo l\u1eafng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00fac n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c \u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 'th\u00e9p' Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng v\u1eabn \u0111ang t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ed5 ch\u00e2n g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 6. T\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo l\u1eddi c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u0129, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t 3 tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf t\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997, khi m\u00e0 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n trong 10 ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua v\u1edbi th\u1eddi gian n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp trung n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 23/7 t\u1edbi, ngay sau khi v\u00f2ng 20 V-League k\u1ebft th\u00fac. \u0110\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 3 \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y 7/8 tr\u00ean SV\u0110 QG M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh v\u1edbi 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 v\u1edbi tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vff-bat-ngo-loai-thang-tay-u23-uc-khoi-giai-tu-hung-168-191038.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/vff-bat-ngo-loai-thang-tay-u23-uc-khoi-giai-tu-hung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vff-bat-ngo-loai-thang-tay-u23-uc-khoi-giai-tu-hung-168-191038.html\">VFF b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd lo\u1ea1i th\u1eb3ng tay U23 \u00dac kh\u1ecfi gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng</span><br>\r\nL\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eddi tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam song cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0110T U23 \u00dac \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i do kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ph\u00eda VFF.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/dtqg/u23-viet-nam-nam-chung-bang-voi-nhat-ban-tai-asiad-2018-292-190436.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/3/u23-viet-nam-nam-chung-bang-voi-nhat-ban-tai-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/dtqg/u23-viet-nam-nam-chung-bang-voi-nhat-ban-tai-asiad-2018-292-190436.html\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nU23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 khi c\u00f9ng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D v\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn khi hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Th\u1ea7y Park s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5m V\u0103n L\u00e2m hay B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng cho ASIAD 2018?</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Nh\u01b0ng li\u1ec7u HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn ai b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh cho \u0110T Olympic...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4159","checkdouble":"191049"},{"date":"17:48 12/07","title":"Ronaldo sang Juve: Qu\u00e2n domino tr\u00ean TTCN \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/12/ronaldo-sang-juve-quan-domino-tren-ttcn-da-do.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u00edch n\u1ed5 h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t bom t\u1ea5n.\r\n</h2><h2>T\u1eeb s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a CR7<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec1u 50 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng/m\u00f9a, Juventus \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00f3n qu\u00e0 l\u1edbn. Nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Real Madrid &ndash; d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chia tay Ronaldo trong \u00eam \u0111\u1eb9p.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00e1o gi\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Perez, \u00f4ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m g\u00ec n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc. N\u00f3i c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c, K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng s\u1ebd t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf ng\u00f4i sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean v\u1eeba xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, v\u1eeba n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i t\u1eeb cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi gi\u1edd, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu s\u1ebd l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Neymar.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng theo tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Marca x\u00e1c th\u1ef1c, Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i th\u00f4ng tin h\u1ecfi mua Neymar v\u00e0 Kylian Mbappe &ndash; nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 th\u1ee9 hai th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. V\u00ec v\u1eady, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 kh\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n &ldquo;th\u1ea3 th\u00ednh&rdquo; trong th\u1eddi gian qua &ndash; Eden Hazard.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus Qu\u00e2n Domino \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus Qu\u00e2n Domino \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/rod.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus s\u1ebd k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t bom t\u1ea5n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nSau nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng chi ti\u1ec1n v\u00e0 k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n (k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb Gareth Bale), Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i chu k\u1ef3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169. Cristiano Ronaldo cho h\u1ecd c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. V\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed7i CR7, Real \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch thay m\u00e1u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Luka Modric. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 Lazio \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecfi mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Savic v\u00e0 Hazard ch\u0103ng n\u1eefa, K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f9 \u0111\u1eafp l\u1ea1i s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ronaldo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t &ldquo;si\u00eau nh\u00e2n&rdquo; 2 trong 1, ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c anh ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb&hellip; Messi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Real bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i chi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh cho c\u1ea3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u La Liga. M\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 chia tay Neymar v\u00e0 n\u0103m nay l\u00e0 CR7, Los Blancos c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh n\u00e0y b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng bom t\u1ea5n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus Qu\u00e2n Domino \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Ronaldo \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn t\u1edbi Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/CHINH-THUC-Cristiano-Ronaldo-toi-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb di\u1ec5n ra</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>Qu\u00e2n domino \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Eden Hazard ra \u0111i, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a chu\u1ed7i chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng mang t\u00ean CR7. Chelsea t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y, ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Trong \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Jorginho t\u1eeb tay Man City, v\u00e0 \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Sarri. Khi m\u1ed9t thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn, h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed1ng ti\u1ec1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi ra \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Juventus, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng cho Ronaldo, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i thu chi v\u00ec lu\u1eadt c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh. Con s\u1ed1 112 tri\u1ec7u euro, c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam 30 tri\u1ec7u euro/m\u00f9a l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn, v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1edbt nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng m\u1edbi \u0111em v\u1ec1 Emre Can v\u1edbi ph\u00ed CNTD, b\u00f9 l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u01a1ng ng\u1ea5t ng\u01b0\u1edfng trong \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gonzalo Higuain \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Chelsea, trong khi Paulo Dybala c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Juve kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i &ldquo;nu\u00f4i&rdquo; c\u1ea3 3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 t\u1ed1n k\u00e9m nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, khi \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u00e1i t\u00ean t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Ronaldo. Ho\u1eb7c n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1eef c\u1ea3 3, nh\u1eefng Mario Mandzukic v\u00e0 Alex Sandro s\u1ebd b\u1eadt b\u00e3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus Qu\u00e2n Domino \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Higuain l\u1ea5y Morata\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/chelsea-vuot-mat-con-moi-vi-real-madrid.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 2 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nV\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 2 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Man United &ndash; \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 2 t\u00e2n binh, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ecfa m\u00e3n trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y. Khi Chelsea, Man United v\u00e0 Man City (\u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 Mahrez) mua s\u1eafm, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean Liverpool c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng nh\u00ecn. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u0103m nay c\u1ee7a Premier League s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi di\u1ec5n ra, v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn c\u00e0ng ph\u1ea3i nhanh ch\u00e2n k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Cris Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus, c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi World Cup 2018 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng tr\u0103m tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/goc-nhin-cristiano-ronaldo-gia-nhap-juventus-176-190940.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: V\u00ec b\u1ecb M.U ph\u1ee5 b\u1ea1c, Ronaldo m\u1edbi \u0111i theo &ldquo;B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m&rdquo; Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-se-chieu-mo-cau-thu-nao-sau-khi-chia-tay-ronaldo-180-190984.html\">Real Madrid s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o sau khi chia tay Ronaldo?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-toi-juventus-muon-ban-higuain-176-191019.html\">Ronaldo t\u1edbi, ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Juventus chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ph\u1ea3i &ldquo;cu\u1ed1n g\u00f3i&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/quan-diem-cristiano-ronaldo-toi-juventus-va-su-ngan-can-cua-mourinho-mu-172-191022.html\">Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: &ldquo;K\u1ebb hai m\u1eb7t&rdquo; Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 ng\u0103n Ronaldo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-thua-nuoc-duc-tha-cau-vu-ronaldo-toi-juventus-172-191026.html\">Liverpool th\u1eeba n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ee5c th\u1ea3 c\u00e2u v\u1ee5 Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/infographics/infographics-cristiano-ronaldo-chia-tay-real-madrid-ra-di-de-lai-nhung-gi-406-190961.html\">Infographics: Cristiano Ronaldo chia tay Real Madrid - Ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4158","checkdouble":"191051"},{"date":"15:32 12/07","title":"Sao 40 tri\u1ec7u Euro n\u00f3i g\u00ec ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Barca?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/12/arthur-phat-bieu-ngay-gia-nhap-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arthur ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ng\u00e0y gia nh\u1eadp Barca. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 40 tri\u1ec7u Euro kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edbi ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb7c \u00e2n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Arthur gia nh\u1eadp Barca</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018, Barca \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arthur t\u1eeb Gremio. H\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Brazil qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1edbi h\u1ebft m\u00f9a 2017/18 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f3n anh. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Arthur, Barca s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 40 tri\u1ec7u Euro t\u00ednh c\u1ea3 ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed ph\u00e1t sinh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nArthur \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Brazil. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 s\u1ebd tr\u00f2n 22 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch ban b\u1eadt m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arthur ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ng\u00e0y gia nh\u1eadp Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arthur ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ng\u00e0y gia nh\u1eadp Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/arthur-phat-bieu-ngay-gia-nhap-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Arthur ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ng\u00e0y gia nh\u1eadp Barca v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nT\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edbi Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Arthur \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Camp Nou ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf v\u00e0 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 6 n\u0103m. Trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f9ng Gremio gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Copa Libertadores b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi. &ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi c\u00f2n nh\u1ecf&rdquo;, anh n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Barca TV.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Barca l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 v\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. C\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u0110\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y vinh d\u1ef1.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang ra Barca d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 Arthur ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i cho Gremio trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00edch l\u0169y th\u00eam kinh nghi\u1ec7m. Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Paulinho (tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u H\u1eb1ng \u0110\u1ea1i) \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ecb thay \u0111\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/everton-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-hang-thai-barca-voi-gia-24-trieu-bang-180-190953.html\">Everton \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 24 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/psg-chi-270-trieu-euro-mua-coutinho-180-190772.html\">C\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c: PSG chi 270 tri\u1ec7u euro mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-paulinho-roi-barca-chi-sau-11-thang-180-190739.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Paulinho \u0111i th\u1eadt xa \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1... Trung Qu\u1ed1c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/neymar-muon-psg-rut-ruot-barca-180-190707.html\">Neymar mu\u1ed1n PSG r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/day-4-muc-tieu-sieu-khung-duoc-barca-nham-nang-cap-tuyen-giua-180-190595.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! 4 M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca nh\u1eafm n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4157","checkdouble":"191037"},{"date":"15:04 12/07","title":"Liverpool th\u1eeba n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ee5c th\u1ea3 c\u00e2u v\u1ee5 Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/liverpool-thua-nuoc-duc-tha-cau-vu-ronaldo-toi-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Paulo Dybala t\u1eeb Juventus, The Kop \u0111ang tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin s\u1ebd b\u00e1n m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn sau khi \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Ronaldo t\u1eeb Real Madrid.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool chi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Dybala</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u Real Madrid x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-real-xac-nhan-ronaldo-cap-ben-juventus-180-190888.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</span>. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1985 \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin, h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng 30 tri\u1ec7u euro/m\u00f9a. \u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 khi\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Paulo Dybala t\u1eeb Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Paulo Dybala t\u1eeb Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/7/Chi-80-trieu-bang,-Liverpool-muon-mua-Paulo-Dybala-tu-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Dybala&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nJuventus \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 105 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Ronaldo, v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Gonzalo Higuain \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin. CR7 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap &ldquo;B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0&rdquo; nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Paulo Dybala t\u1eeb Juventus, The Kop \u0111ang tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin s\u1ebd b\u00e1n m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn sau khi \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Ronaldo t\u1eeb Real Madrid.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Klopp \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Dybala v\u00e0 tin r\u1eb1ng anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 Coutinho \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn n\u00e0y s\u1ebd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Juventus b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Liverpool c\u00f3 Dybala</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, song kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Liverpool c\u00f3 Dybala v\u1eabn \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Juventus kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u01b0u ti\u00ean gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dybala len tieng moi chao Ronaldo\" title=\"Dybala l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng m\u1eddi ch\u00e0o Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/liverpool-thua-nuoc-duc-tha-cau-vu-ronaldo-toi-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Dybala mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Ronaldo \u1edf Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Dybala \u0111\u00e3 ghi t\u1edbi 23 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 7 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 37 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 Serie A tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi Ronaldo.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJuventus s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Gonzalo Higuain ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 Dybala. Hi\u1ec7n Chelsea l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y khi bi\u1ebft tin Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus, Dybala kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: &ldquo;Ch\u00e0o m\u1eebng anh \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Juventus, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f9ng Ronaldo thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn. H\u00f4m nay l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y vui v\u1edbi NHM Juventus&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4156","checkdouble":"191026"},{"date":"15:53 12/07","title":"V\u1ee5 HLV Sarri \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea c\u00f3 di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/31/vu-hlv-sarri-den-chelsea-co-dien-bien-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Maurizio Sarri t\u1edbi Chelsea thay Antonio Conte s\u1eafp c\u00f3 h\u1ed3i k\u1ebft, h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u1edd b\u00e1o c\u1ee7a Italia \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Blues s\u1ebd b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 chi 6 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a HLV Maurizio Sarri v\u1edbi Napoli, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho Antonio Conte. Napoli c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Ancelotti thay \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 HLV Maurizio Sarri t\u1edbi Chelsea s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 HLV Maurizio Sarri t\u1edbi Chelsea s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/31/vu-hlv-sarri-den-chelsea-co-dien-bien-moi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea s\u1eafp b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Maurizio Sarri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n l\u00e0 s\u1ebd b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri thay Conte v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 6, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mang t\u00ean \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed HLV Conte \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Maurizio Sarri t\u1edbi Chelsea thay Antonio Conte s\u1eafp c\u00f3 h\u1ed3i k\u1ebft, h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u1edd b\u00e1o c\u1ee7a Italia \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Blues s\u1ebd b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p bu\u1ed9c Conte t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Chelsea ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn sa th\u1ea3i c\u1ef1u HLV Juventus, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec1n 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi c\u00f9ng l\u00fac</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Daily Mail, Chelsea s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 c\u00f9ng l\u00fac 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. Ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c \u00f4ng b\u1ed1 HLV Sarri ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Conte, The Blues c\u00f2n c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng Jorginho t\u1eeb Napoli.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jorginho nhieu kha nang se toi Chelsea\" title=\"Jorginho nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/jo-2.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jorginho l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Anh, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00f4m qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1eaft g\u1eb7p \u1edf s\u00e2n bay, anh \u0111ang l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Anh k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-sao-khung-serie-a-bay-sang-anh-ky-hop-dong-voi-dai-gia-premier-league-172-190983.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mua Jorginho </span>th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Man City trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0 Napoli y\u00eau c\u1ea7u, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Man City ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 44 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Jorginho t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge theo ti\u1ebfng g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Sarri.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 m\u1ea5t 58 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Sarri v\u00e0 Jorginho, sau khi c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 hai th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Daniele Rugani t\u1eeb Juventus. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Blues \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua trung v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4155","checkdouble":"191036"},{"date":"16:08 12/07","title":"PSG v\u00e0 Juventus nh\u0103m nhe th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/psg-va-juventus-muon-mua-brewster-sao-tre-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>PSG v\u00e0 Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Brewster, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh. \u0110\u1ebfn nay, sao tr\u1ebb 18 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi The Kop.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n sao tr\u1ebb</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRhian Brewster \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ph\u1ea3i bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh sau khi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U17 World Cup di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9 cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m 2017. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, sao tr\u1ebb sinh n\u0103m 2000 ghi t\u1edbi 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn gi\u00fap U17 Anh gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBrewster hi\u1ec7n thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Liverpool. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn nay anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u1edbi CLB n\u00e0y. Liverpool \u0111ang s\u1ed1t s\u1eafng m\u1edf c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"PSG v\u00e0 Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Brewster th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"PSG v\u00e0 Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Brewster th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/PSG-va-Juventus-muon-mua-Brewster-than-dong-cua-Liverpool-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Brewster gi\u00e0nh gi\u1ea3i Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup U17</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u Brewster mong mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0 ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean cho \u0111\u1ed9i 1. \u0110\u1ebfn nay, Liverpool v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u tr\u00ean c\u1ee7a ch\u00e0ng trai sinh t\u1ea1i London trong khi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o t\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a anh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>PSG v\u00e0 Juventus nh\u0103m nhe cu\u1ed7m Brewster</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Liverpool ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c sao tr\u1ebb \u1edf l\u1ea1i, xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng tin PSG v\u00e0 Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Brewster. Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i tr\u00ean ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n b\u1ecf m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00ed \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o cho The Kop.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Brewster cua liverpool\" title=\"Brewster cua liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/psg-va-juventus-muon-mua-brewster-sao-tre-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>PSG v\u00e0 Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Brewster</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u00ednh nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i \u1edf tr\u00ean, Brewster mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec9nh cao. PSG \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh song v\u1eabn \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nJuventus sau khi c\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1eabn \u0111ang d\u00f5i theo di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Brewster. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Brewster \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Borussia Dortmund v\u00e0 RB Leipzig \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 anh. Ngo\u00e0i PSG v\u00e0 Juventus, c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng Arsenal, Tottenham, Barcelona v\u00e0 Monaco c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau d\u1ee5 Brewster v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-van-muon-mua-grealish-172-190672.html\">Liverpool ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u0103n sao tr\u1ebb h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-khong-con-co-hoi-chieu-mo-fekir-172-190670.html\">Liverpool kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Fekir</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-chi-ky-chap-nhan-giai-cuu-shaqiri-neu-172-190604.html\">Liverpool ch\u1ec9 k\u00fd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u Shaqiri n\u1ebfu...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thuc-hu-vu-klopp-muon-liverpool-mua-xherdan-shaqiri-172-190490.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Klopp mu\u1ed1n Liverpool mua Xherdan Shaqiri</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/fabinho-khang-dinh-chua-tung-tien-gan-mu-172-190409.html\">Fabinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ee5t v\u1edbi MU</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4154","checkdouble":"191041"},{"date":"16:43 12/07","title":"Chelsea b\u1ecb t\u00e2n binh NHA qua m\u1eb7t v\u1ee5 \u201cXavi ch\u00e2u Phi\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/giot-nuoc-mat-tre-tho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Fulham s\u1eafp mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Jean-Michael Seri t\u1eeb Nice. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1edfi ai c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 Chelsea m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Seri</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a 2017/18 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Jean-Michael Seri th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i Nice. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng (ch\u1ec9 cao 1m68) nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu s\u1ee9c b\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng, t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSeri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t &ldquo;c\u1ee7a hi\u1ebfm&rdquo; c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u Phi. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m b\u00f3ng l\u00e0 s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd tr\u00f2n 27 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 19/7 t\u1edbi v\u00e0 gi\u00fap anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Xavi Hernandez c\u1ee7a Barcelona.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fulham s\u1eafp mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Jean-Michael Seri t\u1eeb Nice h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Fulham s\u1eafp mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Jean-Michael Seri t\u1eeb Nice h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/Fulham-sap-mua-duoc-Jean-Michael-Seri-tu-Nice-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u00f9ng nh\u1eb1ng Conte v\u00e0 Sarri khi\u1ebfn Chelsea kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng qua, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tin Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Jean-Michael Seri. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u1ed1t HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u00f9a sau c\u00f2n Arsenal chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n Lucas Torreira t\u1eeb Sampdoria. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n xao nh\u00e3ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 v\u1edbi Seri.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Fulham s\u1eafp l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nFulham s\u1eafp mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Jean-Michael Seri t\u1eeb Nice. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i h\u1ecd c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Aston Villa \u1edf chung k\u1ebft play-off gi\u00fap Fulham \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00ean ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a 2018/19.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Jean-Michael Seri\" title=\"tien ve Jean-Michael Seri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/giot-nuoc-mat-tre-tho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Fulham s\u1eafp mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Jean-Michael Seri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ecd \u0111ang r\u00e1o ri\u1ebft thay m\u00e1u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh nh\u1eb1m chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Seri, Fulham c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n mang v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Maxime Le Marchand c\u1ee7a anh t\u1ea1i Nice. Le Marchand c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i trung v\u1ec7 l\u1eabn h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Slavisa Jokanovic c\u00f3 th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSong song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mua Seri, Fulham \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng mua \u0111\u1ee9t Aleksandar Mitrovic t\u1eeb Newcastle. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Serbia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i Fulham m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 17 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n. Ngo\u00e0i ra, The Cottage c\u0169ng \u0111ang li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Dedryck Boyata c\u1ee7a Celtic.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/fulham-len-hang-premier-league-201819-172-187102.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/27/fulham-len-hang-premier-league-201819.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/fulham-len-hang-premier-league-201819-172-187102.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! C\u00e1i t\u00ean cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i Premier League 2018/19</span><br>\r\n<span>Fulham l\u00ean h\u1ea1ng Premier League 2018/19 sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Aston Villa \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft play-off tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Wembley. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Tom Cairney \u0111\u00e3...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4153","checkdouble":"191047"},{"date":"17:11 12/07","title":"\u201cBom t\u1ea5n\u201d 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Riyad Mahrez c\u1ee7a Man City kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp c\u1ee1 n\u00e0o?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/12/bom-tan-60-trieu-bang-riyad-mahrez-cua-man-city-khung-khiep-co-nao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man City mua Riyad Mahrez th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Man xanh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. V\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Mahrez \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf s\u00e2n Etihad.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Mahrez \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m nay, ch\u00ednh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00f2i t\u1edbi Man City l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Riyad Mahrez b\u1ecb Leicester \u0111\u00e0y \u1ea3i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t ti\u1ec1n. D\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian nh\u01b0ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\">\r\n            <h3><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City mua Riyad Mahrez T\u00e2n binh 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng kh\u1ee7ng th\u1ebf n\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Man City mua Riyad Mahrez T\u00e2n binh 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng kh\u1ee7ng th\u1ebf n\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/24/Man-City-mua-Riyad-Mahrez-Tan-binh-60-trieu-bang-khung-the-nao-hinh-anh.jpg\"></h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mahrez c\u00f3 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 10 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, Riyad Mahrez \u0111\u00e3 ghi t\u1edbi 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 10 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a Leicester c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ed9ng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Algeria.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u00ednh ra m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 39% s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Leicester \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, c\u1ee9 trung b\u00ecnh 128,4 ph\u00fat, Mahrez l\u1ea1i in d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a &ldquo;B\u1ea7y c\u00e1o&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSo s\u00e1nh s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng + ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o (22) c\u1ee7a Mahrez \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Man City cho th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, anh x\u1ebfp sau Sterling (29, 18 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, 11 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o), Sane (25, 10 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, 15 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o) v\u00e0 De Bruyne (24, 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, 16 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o) nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean David Silva (20), v\u00e0 Bernardo Silva (10). Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Mahrez c\u00f2n cao h\u01a1n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gabriel Jesus (16).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Leicester, Mahrez ra s\u00e2n 109 trong t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 114 tr\u1eadn t\u1ed1i \u0111a \u1edf Premier League, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a anh l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. Ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng th\u00f4ng minh g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 mi\u1ec5n nhi\u1ec5m v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p li\u00ean t\u1ee5c nh\u01b0 Mahrez, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Man City s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3, Pep Guardiola s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a Mahrez c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2015/16 \u0111\u1ebfn nay, Mahrez \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 35 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 8 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Algeria.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u0169ng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a 2015/16 ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 24 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf Premier League c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o h\u01a1n ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mahrez l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Algeria c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi. K\u1ef9 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef th\u0103ng b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1t gi\u00fap Mahrez d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng 1 \u0111\u1ed1i 1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mahrez co 290 lan qua nguoi thanh cong trong 3 mua giai vua qua o NHA\" title=\"Mahrez c\u00f3 290 l\u1ea7n qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua \u1edf NHA\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/ma.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mahrez c\u00f3 290 l\u1ea7n qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua \u1edf NHA</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111i b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb b\u00ean ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 r\u1ed3i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ho\u1eb7c ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y c\u1ee7a Mahrez trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Leicester.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 290 l\u1ea7n qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Theo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea t\u1eeb Opta, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Eden Hazard, Wilfried Zaha v\u00e0 Alexis Sanchez c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u01a1n t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Man City.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Claude Puel c\u1ee7a Leicester \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Mahrez: &ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i b\u00f3ng \u1edf t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 cao c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i l\u1eafc ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mahrez \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1ef1 \u0111a n\u0103ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mahrez l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Leicester, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 n\u01a1i gi\u00fap Mahrez ph\u00e1t huy h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Riyad Mahrez\" title=\"tien ve Riyad Mahrez\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/Riyad-Mahrez-toi-Arsenal-thay-vi-Man-City-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>S\u1ef1 \u0111a n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Riyad Mahrez s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u cho Pep \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m l\u1ec7ch ph\u1ea3i, ch\u01a1i h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u00e1 &ldquo;s\u1ed1 9 \u1ea3o&rdquo; khi c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede s\u00e2n Etihad, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a Mahrez \u0111ang do Raheem Sterling \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh v\u1eeba c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Anh, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Sterling \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t m\u00ecnh \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Sterling sa s\u00fat phong \u0111\u1ed9 Mahrez c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00f4 h\u1ea1n t\u00e2n binh 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Man xanh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Kevin de Bruyne ho\u1eb7c David Silva ch\u01a1i \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m Mahrez s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Man City, Pep Guardiola c\u0169ng s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 anh h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f9ng kh\u00e1t khao ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh, Mahrez ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Etihad m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/man-city-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-mahrez-172-190895.html\" target=\"_blank\">Man City mua Riyad Mahrez</span> v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 khai th\u00e1c t\u1ed1i \u0111a kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4152","checkdouble":"191050"}]}